OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1777489866
OL,3,C20-year-old Guernsey woman arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of attempted murder
OL,6,FA 20-year-old woman from Guernsey has
OL,7,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fattempted murder.
OL,10,FGuernsey Police say a person is in
OL,11,Fhospital in a serious but stable
OL,12,Fcondition and that investigations are
OL,13,Fongoing at a house on Victoria Avenue
OL,14,Fin St Sampson.
OL,16,FThe force are asking any islanders
OL,17,Fwith relevant information to come
OL,18,Fforward.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
