PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1777489866
OL,3,C20-year-old Guernsey woman arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of attempted murder
OL,6,FIn a statement, Det Supt Jonathan
OL,7,FBancroft, from Guernsey Police, said:
OL,8,F"In the early hours of Sunday morning
OL,9,F(26th April), Guernsey Police arrested
OL,10,Fa 20-year-old woman on suspicion of
OL,11,Fattempted murder.
OL,13,F"One person was urgently transferred
OL,14,Fto hospital. They remain at the PEH in
OL,15,Fa serious but stable condition.
OL,17,F"Today crime scene investigators have
OL,18,Fbeen carrying out work on a property
OL,19,Fin the area of Victoria Avenue, which
OL,20,Fis why there has been an increased
OL,21,Fpolice presence in that area.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1777489866
OL,3,C20-year-old Guernsey woman arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of attempted murder
OL,6,F"Incidents of this nature are
OL,7,Fthankfully very rare occurrences in
OL,8,FGuernsey, and I'd like to take this
OL,9,Fopportunity to reassure islanders that
OL,10,Fwe are not currently searching for any
OL,11,Ffurther suspects. There is no
OL,12,Finformation at present that suggests
OL,13,Fany wider risk.
OL,15,F"Enquiries are now ongoing, and anyone
OL,16,Fwith any relevant information is asked
OL,17,Fto contact the Criminal Investigation
OL,18,FDepartment by calling 01481 222 222,
OL,19,For to call Crimestoppers anonymously
OL,20,Fon 0800 555 111."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
